'''OpenCore'''是一个安全且轻量化的[[Hackintosh|黑苹果]]開放原始碼[[引导|引导]]方式。最初诞生于HermitCrabs实验室，现由Acidanthera运营。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=精解OpenCore|url=https://blog.daliansky.net/OpenCore-BootLoader.html|accessdate=2020-07-20|work=黑果小兵的部落阁|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720003640/https://blog.daliansky.net/OpenCore-BootLoader.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.muycomputer.com/2020/06/14/OpenCore-hackintosh-apple/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128164232/https://www.muycomputer.com/2020/06/14/OpenCore-hackintosh-apple/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

OpenCore目前处于公测阶段，截至2022年4月，其最新正式版为0.8.0。相比于[[Clover_(啟動程式)|Clover]]，OpenCore的[[配置文件|配置文件]]更为简单。（仅限于在两种引导的编译方式都为文本时）<ref>{{Cite web|title=OpenCore官方文档|url=https://dortania.github.io/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720072837/https://dortania.github.io/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

從OpenCore衍生一個名為「[[OpenCore_Legacy_Patcher|OpenCore Legacy Patcher]]」的軟體專案，目的是讓不支援[[Metal_(API)|Metal API]]的舊款[[麥金塔|麥金塔]]也能安裝[[MacOS_Mojave|MacOS Mojave]]暨後續版本之[[macOS|macOS]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Dortania |title=OpenCore Legacy Patcher |url=https://dortania.github.io/OpenCore-Legacy-Patcher/ |access-date=2022-03-01 |archive-date=2022-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419142354/https://dortania.github.io/OpenCore-Legacy-Patcher/ }}</ref>。

